    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve shim adjustment were recently completed. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior displays some light road-use patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing the tactile, analog feedback expected of this chassis. This is a mechanically sorted machine ready for spirited canyon runs or track-day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
