    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury SUV represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, though light creasing is visible on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, from the panoramic sunroof to the navigation system, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust; it has been serviced exclusively at authorized intervals, with a fresh oil change and comprehensive multi-point inspection recently completed. The tires have significant tread life remaining, ensuring a smooth, quiet, and confident ride. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle for a discerning buyer who appreciates a well-documented history and a clean, smoke-free interior.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
