    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it is honestly such a great find. It\u2019s been super well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a reliable, smooth ride without the brand-new price tag. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it! If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks sharp on the road, you've gotta come check this one out. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 33500.0,
