    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the powerband. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its signature 50/50 weight distribution, offering precise turn-in and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains tight and the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. A perfect specimen for the driver who prioritizes analog performance and mechanical pedigree.",
